strings.Value: "So, rations for lunch today? â€” Great! I've got dried apples!"
"Why is everyone so gloomy? So we have rations for supper, big deal. Is that really a good reason to be so sad?"
"Without fresh meat it's not a meal. It's just crap!"
"Oh, times like these I miss the good old days, when a proper chef cooked for me."
"Good grief! Even Octavia can see how many rations we've got left. I guess that must mean you could count them on one hand."
"The light of your heart warms those around you. Traveling with you is a true pleasure!"
